Package: rdnnmcshap
Title: DNN-Monte Carlo-Shapley Framework for Health Insurance Cost Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Thabang Bongani Junior", "Baloyi",
           email = "2015015486@ufs4life.ac.za",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R interface to the dnnmcshap Python package via reticulate.
    Implements a three-stage framework combining Deep Neural Network
    prediction, Monte Carlo simulation and Shapley value attribution
    for understanding health insurance cost drivers.
